Package: nightlightstats
Type: Package
Title: nightlightstats
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Jakob Miethe, Mark Toth
Maintainer: Jakob Miethe <jakob.miethe@econ.lmu.de>, Mark Toth <mark-toth@uni-bonn.de>
Description: This R package allows for calculating user-specified statistics on nighttime light satellite data. The package processes yearly DMSP (Defense Meteorological Satellite Program) data ranging from 1992 to 2013 and monthly VIIRS (Visible Infrared Imaging Radiometer Suite) data beginning in April 2012.
License: GPL-3 + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
